665
00:39:34,060 --> 00:39:41,060
 Lord, for those of us that find words difficult, I pray you give us words.

666
00:39:41,060 --> 00:39:47,060
 But for all of us, Lord, you'll help us to be the people of God,

667
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:54,060
 to act like Jesus, to be the hands and feet of Jesus to our colleagues and our workmates.

668
00:39:54,060 --> 00:40:00,060
 I want to pray a blessing over you.

669
00:40:00,060 --> 00:40:04,060
 May the love of God sustain us in our working.

670
00:40:04,060 --> 00:40:08,060
 May the light of Jesus radiate our thinking and our speaking.

671
00:40:08,060 --> 00:40:11,060
 May the power of the Spirit penetrate all our deliberating.

672
00:40:13,060 --> 00:40:18,060
 May all that is done witness to your presence in our life.

673
00:40:18,060 --> 00:40:23,060
 We want to have a period now where we pray for each other,

674
00:40:23,060 --> 00:40:26,060
 where we open this up.

675
00:40:26,060 --> 00:40:32,060
 I just want to ask, if you were in any of those three groups I mentioned,

676
00:40:32,060 --> 00:40:37,060
 if you're a young person wondering what's next, where is my way in life,

677
00:40:37,060 --> 00:40:42,060
 if you're somewhat older and thinking about a career change,

678
00:40:42,060 --> 00:40:46,060
 or if you're about a job, I'm going to ask you to do something really, really bold now,

679
00:40:46,060 --> 00:40:47,060
 just while we're here.

680
00:40:47,060 --> 00:40:49,060
 Can you just put your hand up because we're going to pray for you,

681
00:40:49,060 --> 00:40:50,060
 if you're in those categories.

682
00:40:50,060 --> 00:40:53,060
 There are people all around the place, right?

683
00:40:53,060 --> 00:40:56,060
 Everybody else, you're on the ministry team.

684
00:40:56,060 --> 00:41:02,060
 Can you look for these people with their hands up as the band play in the background,

685
00:41:02,060 --> 00:41:04,060
 and can you go and pray God's blessing on them?

686
00:41:04,060 --> 00:41:07,060
 Keep your hands up high because we don't want you to miss out on prayer here.

687
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:08,060
 We're going to come and pray for you now.

688
00:41:09,060 --> 00:41:12,060
 If that's you, we're going to pray for you upper house as well.

689
00:41:12,060 --> 00:41:14,060
 Look for the people around you.

690
00:41:14,060 --> 00:41:18,060
 This is not something for us to opt out of.

691
00:41:18,060 --> 00:41:22,060
 If you're near someone, go and lay hands on them, and pray for them,

692
00:41:22,060 --> 00:41:24,060
 and pray for God to move in their life.

693
00:41:24,060 --> 00:41:26,060
 And we thank you.

694
00:41:26,060 --> 00:41:28,060
 Thank you Lord for what you're doing.

695
00:41:28,060 --> 00:41:32,060
 Let's just step out and pray.

